videos.description: Bengals Jeremy Hill snapped back to form rushing for three TDs in Cincinnati's 36-21 win, earning him a game ball from ESPN Bengals reporter Coley Harvey. Chiefs kicker Cairo Santos received one from Chiefs reporter Adam Teicher after a seven-FG effort.
videos.headline: Hill's bounce-back day and Santos' 7 field goals earn game balls
